8
00:00:32,074 --> 00:00:33,564
♪ and I can't describe
the room ♪

9
00:00:33,784 --> 00:00:36,901
♪ but the atmosphere
is warm and dear ♪

10
00:00:37,120 --> 00:00:40,829
♪ with the friendly whippoorwill
singing on her windowsill ♪

11
