♪ shh! Susan slept here ♪

12
00:00:45,128 --> 00:00:48,211
♪ sunlight kisses her shoulder ♪

13
00:00:48,423 --> 00:00:51,711
♪ that's one light
I'm jealous of ♪

14
00:00:51,927 --> 00:00:55,636
♪ mirror, mirror, mirror,
jealous 'cause youre near her ♪

15
